    "Figure 18 shows the distribution of their usage in the articles.",
    "It is revealed that while some studies implement only one dataset, some others implement multiple datasets.",
    "DEAP is used in more than half of the articles (N = 68, 57%).",
    "Following, the SEED (N = 27, %23), MAHNOB-HCI (N = 7, 6%) and DREAMER (N = 3, 2%) databases are used.",
    "In addition, 12 percent of the articles (N = 15) use some other databases such as eNTERFACE, SEED-VI or self-generated datasets."
  ],
